#### ============================================================
#### Working with Dewey Data in R
#### Advan Neighborhood Patterns Plus — Reproducible Guide
#### Dewey Data · 2026
#### ============================================================
## A practical supplement to Dewey's "Working with R" documentation.
## Covers downloading, loading, exploring, and visualizing a
## date-partitioned parquet dataset end-to-end.
##
## Demonstrated dataset: Advan Neighborhood Patterns Plus
## Geographic coverage: US and Canada CBGs, monthly, 2019–present.
##
## Adapt download parameters, column selection, filters, and
## visuals to any Dewey dataset and research question.
#### ============================================================


